name: Kino
definition: Use kino to test her compliance.

name: Favor
definition: Ask her to do you a favor.
examples: Ask her to hold your drink.
Hand her money and have her buy you a drink.

name: Screening
definition: Ask screening questions to qualify her.

name: Reverse
definition: Reverse the request before you do it.
examples: Will you buy me a drink? - Buy me a drink and we'll see.
